{"id":128620,"type":6,"name":"荃加福祿壽探案","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/7e/58/128620_ldLtT.jpg","summary":"　某年冬至的寒夜，三個本來應該沒半點聯繫的小孩：恭犢嵐(阮兆祥飾)、恭澤嵐(王祖藍飾)和崔湑(李思捷飾)，在一間破屋裡遇上，三人一見如故，各自許下願望：犢嵐希望變得「好打」、澤嵐希望可以穿牆過壁、崔湑希望所有女人會跟他講真話。犢嵐、澤嵐質疑心願望能否成真，崔湑篤定的吹噓，只要你肯相信，任何東西都可以成真。這一夜，三人分別後就各散東西，各自生活卻出現重大轉變……","info":"<li><span>中文名: </span>荃加福禄寿探案</li><li><span>放送星期: </span>星期一至五 20:30－21:30</li><li><span>监制: </span><a href=\"/person/17033\">關永忠</a></li><li><span>编审: </span>潘漫紅、<a href=\"/person/16650\">梁恩東</a></li><li><span>主题歌演出: </span><a href=\"/person/16599\">汪明荃</a>、<a href=\"/person/17004\">阮兆祥</a>、<a href=\"/person/17036\">王祖藍</a>、<a href=\"/person/17877\">李思捷</a>《超低能》</li><li><span>主演: </span><a href=\"/person/16599\">汪明荃</a>、<a href=\"/person/17036\">王祖藍</a>、<a href=\"/person/17004\">阮兆祥</a>、<a href=\"/person/17877\">李思捷</a>、<a href=\"/person/17392\">梁靖琪</a></li><li><span>别名: </span>Super Snoops</li><li><span>集数: </span>20</li><li><span>开始: </span>2011-10-03</li><li><span>结束: </span>2011-10-28</li><li><span>类型: </span>懷舊查案喜劇</li><li><span>国家/地区: </span>香港</li><li><span>电视台: </span>TVB</li><li><span>官方网站: </span>programme.tvb.com/drama/supersnoops</li><li><span>编剧: </span>林麗媚、曾保華、陳琪、黃秉怡、谷軒龍、譚劍偉</li><li><span>制作年份: </span>2011年2月－5月</li><li><span>制作统筹: </span>伍詠詩</li><li><span>制作公司: </span>香港電視廣播有限公司</li>","collection":{"collect":2},"tags":[{"name":"港剧","count":2},{"name":"TVB","count":1},{"name":"2011","count":1}],"eps":[{"id":505494,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/505494","type":0,"sort":1,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":505495,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/505495","type":0,"sort":2,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":505496,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/505496","type":0,"sort":3,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":505497,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/505497","type":0,"sort":4,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"",